{"tid":1509842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「心很累」岩岩遇到個台灣人，係個例外","createTime":"2019-08-27T03:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T03:48:55.000Z","uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35131b18ab80f7f40de1efadea9bd173b463592e","tid":1509842,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"話說我岩岩見到個台灣人，立場係奶共而且有知識...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係大陸同香港做野<br />\n佢一嚟做話先唔好講警察點點點<br />\n咁其實可以唔洗載口罩<br />\n載左口罩個人係會大膽好多點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他國家都有蒙臉法，美國、加拿大、歐洲好多都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢覺條例冇咩問題，台灣一早就有送中條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話就算要送上去都要香港呢邊審左先<br />\n我就話條條例唔合理、唔完善<br />\n減左範圍、升左刑期，佢就話咁係想多啲去定少啲人送翻上去<br />\n我講佢就係咁駁<br />\n跟住我就講社會評分系統，佢話咁監控嘅係政府<br />\n如果係美國就係私人，資料就係互通，係一間公司被人炒左，另一間就唔會請你，保險都係所以有啲人成世都買唔到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話香港發展緩慢左，佢就話全世界都係，只少香港嘅人工都有高到，台灣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最想死嘅一句係，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全世界發展緩慢左係因為要等大陸發展先</span></span><br />\n水漲船高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Wtfffffffff</span></span> <br />\n搞唔掂，佢811前一日飛到覺得自己好好彩<br />\n屌你，自私撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0103c10ec0615ce01785a22da26aec729480a95a","tid":1509842,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbn